snippet.title: Super Mario Eclipse | Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The date is set! We can't wait to get this out the door for everyone to enjoy. Have a great Christmas!

We've got a demo out now! - https://gamebanana.com/mods/432762
Come visit us on Discord - https://discord.gg/u6NHuHVRpJ
Song link - https://youtu.be/JUfdcfXO7ws?si=AbbxGDz6ecThaeGd
Watch the Demo 2 trailer - https://youtu.be/JTiCPEY39M4

Editing and effects by - @UncleMeatz 
Music by - @ShaneMGD 
Gameplay footage by - @epicwade6346
